com.ibm.team.repository.common.query

Interface IItemQueryPage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IQueryPage

    public interface IItemQueryPage
extends IQueryPage

    Represents the definition of a query page for item queries. Results from an item query are a list of zero or more IItemHandles.

    Since:
    0.5
    See Also:
    IQueryPage
